<div class="min-h-screen bg-[#1e1e1e] text-white p-8">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <header class="mb-12">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-2" style="font-family: 'Pretendard', sans-serif;">RapiDeck</h1>
      <p class="text-gray-400">AI로 빠르게 만드는 전문가 수준의 슬라이드</p>
    </header>

    <% if flash[:error] %>
      <div class="bg-red-500/10 border border-red-500 text-red-300 px-4 py-3 rounded mb-6">
        <%= flash[:error] %>
      </div>
    <% end %>

    <% if flash[:warning] %>
      <div class="bg-yellow-500/10 border border-yellow-500 text-yellow-300 px-4 py-3 rounded mb-6">
        <%= flash[:warning] %>
      </div>
    <% end %>

    <%= form_with url: slides_path, method: :post, class: "space-y-6" do |f| %>
      <div>
        <label class="block text-lg font-semibold mb-2">문서 입력</label>
        <textarea
          name="document"
          rows="15"
          class="w-full bg-[#2d2d2d] border border-gray-700 rounded-lg p-4 text-white focus:border-cyan-500 focus:ring-1 focus:ring-cyan-500 outline-none transition"
          placeholder="여기에 슬라이드로 만들 문서를 붙여넣어주세요...&#10;&#10;예시:&#10;# 제목&#10;## 소제목&#10;내용..."
          required
        ></textarea>
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-2">최대 30페이지까지 처리됩니다 (약 15,000자)</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <label class="block text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Gemini API 키</label>
        <input
          type="text"
          name="api_key"
          class="w-full bg-[#2d2d2d] border border-gray-700 rounded-lg p-4 text-white focus:border-cyan-500 focus:ring-1 focus:ring-cyan-500 outline-none transition"
          placeholder="AIzaSy..."
          required
        >
        <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-2">
          <a href="https://aistudio.google.com/app/apikey" target="_blank" class="text-cyan-500 hover:text-cyan-400 underline">
            Google AI Studio
          </a>에서 무료로 발급받을 수 있습니다
        </p>
      </div>

      <button
        type="submit"
        class="w-full bg-gradient-to-r from-cyan-500 to-blue-500 hover:from-cyan-600 hover:to-blue-600 text-white font-bold py-4 px-6 rounded-lg transition-all transform hover:scale-[1.02] active:scale-[0.98]"
      >
        슬라이드 생성하기
      </button>
    <% end %>

    <div class="mt-12 p-6 bg-[#2d2d2d] rounded-lg border border-gray-700">
      <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-3">💡 사용 팁</h3>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-400">
        <li>• 마크다운 형식을 사용하면 더 좋은 결과를 얻을 수 있습니다</li>
        <li>• 제목, 소제목, 목록 등 구조를 명확히 작성해주세요</li>
        <li>• 슬라이드 생성에는 1-2분 정도 소요됩니다</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
